RGB Belt

After going to enough raves, I finally reallised that I need to bring some arduino powered rgb magic to the show. 
This is my attempt to make the Adafruit RGB belt kit even more awesome by making it sound sentitive.



Projects this was based on:
Adafruit LEDbeltKit_alt example:https://github.com/adafruit/LPD8806/blob/master/examples/LEDbeltKit_alt/LEDbeltKit_alt.pde
VUMeterBelt: https://github.com/Kabong/VUMeterBelt

Parts:
RGB Belt Kit: http://www.adafruit.com/products/332
Mic: http://www.adafruit.com/products/1063
